Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Bejoy Mobile (“we”) respect the privacy of its users (“User” or “You”) and are committed to protect the User’s information, be it yours or your child’s. We believe that You have a right to know our practices regarding the information we may collect and use when You use our mobile applications.
WE DO NOT COLLECT ANY PERSONAL INFORMATION
No personal information is required to download our apps.
No personal information is collected when using our apps.
NON-PERSONAL INFORMATION MAY COLLECTED
Some of our apps integrate advertise service, which may use some Non-Personal Information to deliver better service. Non-Personal Information may include the following technical information:
"    >Type of operation system (e.g. iOS, Android, Windows Phone, etc.)
"    >Screen resolution (e.g. 800×600, 1024×768, etc.)
"    >Language (e.g. English)
"    >Device Vendor (e.g. Galaxy, HTC, iPhone, etc.)
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policies, please contact us:
